<title>USA: STB Systems Inc sets 3-for-2 stock split.</title>
<headline>STB Systems Inc sets 3-for-2 stock split.</headline>
<dateline>RICHARDSON, Texas 1997-06-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>STB Systems Inc said on Friday that it has declared a three-for-two split of the company's common stock, to take the form of a stock dividend.</p>
<p>The dividend will be payable July 17, record June 23, the company said in a statement.</p>
<p>The split is the company's first since its initial public offering in February 1995. STB Systems manufactures multimedia accelerators as well as other multimedia subsystem products.</p>
